The paper discusses a defense mechanism against adversarial examples in image classification systems using deep neural networks. This topic falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), computer security and cryptography (cs.CR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
